snippet.title: Moroi - Official Next Fest Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Steam demo now and descend into the madness of Moroi: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2518410/Moroi/

To escape your eternal torment, fight your way through a perilous labyrinth filled with nightmarish creatures. Whatever path you follow, know that there are several ways that your wretched story might end…

Moroi. Coming to PC in Spring 2025. Wishlist on Steam today!
